{"tid":2401337,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"專家：投資比特幣意味馬斯克絕望，Tesla正面臨前所未有的挑戰！","createTime":"2021-02-09T15:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T22:31:12.000Z","uid":118346,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"273fcb0f4887fbc07d82e9da109cf78ce06a6cbe","tid":2401337,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"美國電動車公司Tesla行政總裁馬斯克曾經在推特（Twitter）大讚比特幣(Bitcoin)，刺激比特幣愈升愈有。GLJ Research分析師Gordon Johnson卻稱，投資比特幣可以看出馬斯克的絕望，因為Tesla正面臨前所未有的挑戰，故他將希望寄託在比特幣上。<br />\n<br />\nGordon Johnson指，Tesla於2020年的三次增發新股中籌集了大量資金，卻將其投資於加密貨幣中。Tesla沒有將籌集的資金充分用於研發及公司發展，比特幣相關新聞出現時，是在Tesla遇到生意發展瓶頸時期出現，可以說是一種誤導或者雜音。<br />\n<br />\nJohnson於報告中列出Tesla三個不利因素，包括中國市場汽車銷量的下降及質量控制問題、德國工廠的停工，以及無法在德國獲得全部12億美元的補貼。Johnson認為，投資比特幣反映出馬斯克的絕望，假如Tesla在今天賣出所有比特幣持倉，該公司將會得到高達2億美元的收益，以抵消汽車業務的虧損。GLJ維持對Tesla「賣出」評級，目標價67美元。<br />\n<br />\n走鬼呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38669cf58de90668aeb5db5aa32c50b44db9fa29","tid":2401337,"uid":18795,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98UAkSv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98UAkSv.png&h=cb20c860&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee23f7ddaa9ff29eb5eead7d1ec40a09ab4d72f6","tid":2401337,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"買得Bitcoin都係生意失敗，唔好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343ddaa0da5355357ff0903f5fb4ea987e605956","tid":2401337,"uid":291491,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"專家應該未上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e84e72eafa9c